OL,3,C'I'm ready to go': Hammer thrower's
OL,4,Clast-minute Commonwealth Games call-up
OL,6,FCumbrian hammer thrower Tara Simpson-
OL,7,FSullivan has announced she will
OL,8,Fcompete at the Commonwealth Games in
OL,9,FGlasgow after a last-minute call-up to
OL,10,FTeam England.
OL,12,FThe 25-year-old from Lowther was told
OL,13,Fshe would replace the injured Anna
OL,14,FPurchase just days before the Games
OL,15,Fstarted.
OL,17,FSimpson-Sullivan won gold at the 2021
OL,18,FBritish Athletics Championships and
OL,19,Fhas a personal best throw of 69.94
OL,20,Fmetres.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
