PN,32302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1784913524
OL,3,C'I'm ready to go': Hammer thrower's
OL,4,Clast-minute Commonwealth Games call-up
OL,6,FGlasgow will be her first senior
OL,7,Finternational competition.
OL,9,FShe said: "It feels great, I'm really
OL,10,Fexcited, it was on my list to get to,
OL,11,Fso I'm ready to go and compete."
OL,13,F"I only found out last week, and then
OL,14,Fgot a confirmation about five days
OL,15,Fago, so it's still very last-minute
OL,16,Ffor me, but this past week has been
OL,17,Fvery difficult keeping it under wraps,
OL,18,Fbut I'm excited now to be able to
OL,19,Fshare that I am going and competing."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
