OL,3,C'I'm ready to go': Hammer thrower's
OL,4,Clast-minute Commonwealth Games call-up
OL,6,FSimpson-Sullivan went to watch the
OL,7,Flast Commonwealth Games held in
OL,8,FGlasgow in 2014, around the time she
OL,9,Ffirst picked up a hammer and could
OL,10,Falready throw it 18 metres.
OL,12,F"I was in athletics for quite a while
OL,13,Fbut one of my team managers had asked:
OL,14,F'can you go throw the hammer, we need
OL,15,Fsome extra points for the team'
OL,17,F"I said: 'I can, but I have no idea
OL,18,Fwhat the hammer is!
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,324,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1784913524
OL,3,C'I'm ready to go': Hammer thrower's
OL,4,Clast-minute Commonwealth Games call-up
OL,6,F"I ended up placing second in my event
OL,7,Fand about four weeks after I qualified
OL,8,Ffor the English Schools' (Athletics
OL,9,FChampionships) and that was me sold -
OL,10,F12 years later, here we are."
OL,12,F"If I manage to make the final on the
OL,13,FTuesday, that would be a massive
OL,14,Fsuccess, and I would love to make the
OL,15,Ffinal (round) of that final - I think
OL,16,Fthat would be absolutely exceptional
OL,17,Ffor me."
OL,19,FSimpson-Sullivan had already planned
OL,20,Fon going to the Games after buying
OL,21,Ftickets to go and watch.
OL,26,@pD@ZpmqD@NpnwD@GpmwD@Mpn
