PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F323A1784913524
OL,3,C'I'm ready to go': Hammer thrower's
OL,4,Clast-minute Commonwealth Games call-up
OL,6,FShe said: "My mum and sister will be
OL,7,Fin the stadium watching from the
OL,8,Fstands, a few friends will be there
OL,9,Fand I know a lot of people will be
OL,10,Fwatching from home too."
OL,12,FThe women's hammer throw qualifying
OL,13,Fwill start at 11:55 on Monday, before
OL,14,Fthe final at 19:55 on Tuesday.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/5
